title: Kim Kardashian Shares New Pics From Her Exciting Trip to Dubai
text: Kim Kardashian Shares New Pics From Her Exciting Trip to Dubai by Zach Seemayer 7:13 PM PST, January 19, 2017 Photo: Instagram Kim Kardashian's trip to Dubai may have come to an end, but she's sharing even more snapshots of the exciting trip to her app and Instagram. The 36-year-old reality star -- who made her first public appearance since her Paris robbery in October at a makeup master class in Dubai last week â€“ spent some time with animals while abroad, getting a chance to practice her falconry as well as ride camels. Photo: KimKardashianWest.com
